content: This seemingly useless file keeps showing up after the build. If that's the case, Is there a way to get rid of it?
ok - I did a search and didn't see an obvious reason that it was being generated
It's from the metadata page in your spreadsheet
The link is there by default. Yank it if you don't want it
I saw lots of similar links in various spreadsheets (not only in Composition). The spreadsheet links make sense, but there is only this one strange non-tracked file that is created by the build.
